Description: Sandstone ostracon: both sides and two edges inscribed with an administrative text, a memorandum ('sḫʒw') concerning the distribution of jars to the members of the work-force at Deir el-Medina.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (136378) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/136378)
